commit_message:
added abstract

added a pdf description of an example use

Bug fixes

super-enhancer annotations should work properly now.

big fix

minor speed improvement fix on Mac OS X systems

newly added mm10 mouse ChIP-Seq peak annotation support.

added support for mouse mm10 peak annotation.
multi-ChIP version now  supports a single ChIP-Seq peaks bed file as a
special case.
Added bound checks for peaks input file.

edited README

added info about the new features

v0.5 beta

Upgraded peak-tool to beta. Now supports list of enhancers from ENCODE,
as well as list of super-enhancers from dbSuper.

Also upgraded peak-tool-multi to support any number of ChIP-Seq peak
files, with the 1st file being the primary and the neighbors elicited
from the rest.
